			<texPath>Things/BA_Students/Weapon/Abydos/ShirokoW</texPath>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
		</graphicData>
		<description>白子的爱用突击步枪。\n一直都在好好地进行整备，所以无论何时都是没有问题的状态。</description>
		<statBases>
			<AccuracyTouch>0.75</AccuracyTouch>
